<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 16:08:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国国防部长奥斯汀自 2022 年 11 月以来首次通话与中国国防部长讨论地区和全球安全问题</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-defence-secretary-austin-discusses-regional-global-security-issues-with-chinese-counterpart-in-first-call-since-november-2022/articleshow/109352371.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109352371.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 15:15:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-defence-secretary-austin-discusses-regional-global-security-issues-with-chinese-counterpart-in-first-call-since-november-2022/articleshow/109352371.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国前领导人利兹·特拉斯在49天后支持特朗普并将其下台归咎于其他人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/former-uk-leader-liz-truss-backs-trump-and-blames-others-for-her-ouster-after-49-days/articleshow/109352311.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109352311.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 15:11:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/former-uk-leader-liz-truss-backs-trump-and-blames-others-for-her-ouster-after-49-days/articleshow/109352311.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰总统签署有争议的法律以加强征兵以抵御俄罗斯的侵略</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukrainian-president-signs-controversial-law-to-boost-conscription-to-fend-off-russias-aggression/articleshow/109352261.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109352261.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;泽连斯基在俄罗斯侵略期间签署了加强征兵的法律，尽管存在财务问题和公众愤怒，但仍提供激励措施。该法律旨在解决缺乏训练有素的士兵的问题，并包括对部队动员计划的修订。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 15:10:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukrainian-president-signs-controversial-law-to-boost-conscription-to-fend-off-russias-aggression/articleshow/109352261.cms</guid></item><item><title>五角大楼：中美防长举行18个月来首次会谈</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-china-defense-chiefs-hold-first-talks-in-18-months-pentagon/articleshow/109351557.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109351557.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;五角大楼表示，美国国防部长周二与中国国防部长进行了通话，这是近 18 个月来超级大国国防部长之间的首次实质性会谈。魏随后被李尚福接替，李尚福去年六月在新加坡举行的一次国防会议上与奥斯汀握手并简短交谈，但没有与五角大楼负责人举行正式会晤。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 14:19:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-china-defense-chiefs-hold-first-talks-in-18-months-pentagon/articleshow/109351557.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗与以色列的冲突使美国的盟友约旦处于紧张状态</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/irans-conflict-with-israel-puts-us-ally-jordan-on-edge/articleshow/109350716.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109350716.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;约旦经历了一段动荡时期，首都举行了支持哈马斯的示威活动，哈马斯是伊朗支持的武装组织，自 10 月初以来在加沙与以色列发生冲突。抗议活动已持续数周，造成巴勒斯坦人伤亡并扰乱生活。 “整个约旦都是哈马斯”和“约旦愤怒日”等口号引起了安全人员的恐慌，导致多人被捕。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 13:49:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/irans-conflict-with-israel-puts-us-ally-jordan-on-edge/articleshow/109350716.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦法院驳回伊姆兰·汗妻子布什拉·比比寻求转移到阿迪亚拉监狱的请求</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-court-disposes-of-imran-khans-wife-bushra-bibis-plea-seeking-transfer-to-adiala-jail/articleshow/109345939.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109345939.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:50:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-court-disposes-of-imran-khans-wife-bushra-bibis-plea-seeking-transfer-to-adiala-jail/articleshow/109345939.cms</guid></item><item><title>面临财务压力，美国宇航局呼吁提出创新提案，以更快、更便宜地将火星岩石带回</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/facing-financial-pressure-nasa-calls-for-innovative-proposals-to-bring-mars-rocks-back-sooner-cheaper/articleshow/109346568.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109346568.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于预算削减，美国宇航局重新评估火星任务，寻求具有成本效益的方法。管理员强调解决方案的紧迫性。毅力号火星车在杰泽罗陨石坑收集了 24 个岩心样本。独立审查批评使命。中国推进火星样本返回。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 11:10:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/facing-financial-pressure-nasa-calls-for-innovative-proposals-to-bring-mars-rocks-back-sooner-cheaper/articleshow/109346568.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国宇航局对袭击佛罗里达州男子家的神秘物体有何评论</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/what-nasa-said-on-mystery-object-that-hit-florida-mans-home/articleshow/109346399.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109346399.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 11:06:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/what-nasa-said-on-mystery-object-that-hit-florida-mans-home/articleshow/109346399.cms</guid></item><item><title>迈克尔·普拉特：你从未听说过的神秘亿万富翁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/michael-platt-the-enigmatic-billionaire-youve-never-heard-of/articleshow/109346229.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109346229.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国首富迈克尔·普拉特 (Michael Platt) 尽管拥有 143 亿英镑的财富，但仍然是个谜。了解更多关于他的秘密生活和在金融界的非凡成功。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 11:04:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/michael-platt-the-enigmatic-billionaire-youve-never-heard-of/articleshow/109346229.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击：以色列对中国的反应“不满”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-attack-israel-unhappy-with-chinas-reaction/articleshow/109346158.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109346158.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列对中国对伊朗袭击的反应感到失望，缺乏预期的支持。美国及其盟国支持以色列，而中国的立场仍然克制。加沙冲突仍在继续，以色列敦促中国影响哈马斯。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:56:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-attack-israel-unhappy-with-chinas-reaction/articleshow/109346158.cms</guid></item><item><title>反以色列抗议者扰乱纽约布鲁克林大桥交通</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/anti-israeli-protesters-disrupt-traffic-on-brooklyn-bridge-in-new-york/articleshow/109346152.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109346152.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:59:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/anti-israeli-protesters-disrupt-traffic-on-brooklyn-bridge-in-new-york/articleshow/109346152.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰称其“导弹用尽”，无法阻止俄罗斯摧毁发电站的袭击</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-says-it-ran-out-of-missiles-to-stop-russian-strike-ruining-power-station/articleshow/109344644.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109344644.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:21:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-says-it-ran-out-of-missiles-to-stop-russian-strike-ruining-power-station/articleshow/109344644.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普将返回纽约刑事法院挑选陪审团</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-to-return-to-new-york-criminal-court-for-jury-selection/articleshow/109344237.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109344237.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 具有里程碑意义的封口费审判已进入第二天，努力选出 12 名纽约市陪审员来决定第一位面临刑事指控的美国前总统的命运。第一天凸显了这项任务的难度，100 名潜在陪审员中约有一半因无法公正地评估这位两极分化的前商人出身的政治家而被原谅。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:18:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-to-return-to-new-york-criminal-court-for-jury-selection/articleshow/109344237.cms</guid></item><item><title>沙特阿拉伯“确认”帮助以色列抵御伊朗袭击</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/saudi-arabia-confirms-helping-israel-against-iranian-attack/articleshow/109344061.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109344061.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;沙特阿拉伯加入了反击伊朗袭击的地区联盟，这对于约旦领空的无人机的防御至关重要。美国在袭击后支持以色列。人们对潜在冲突升级的担忧加剧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:08:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/saudi-arabia-confirms-helping-israel-against-iranian-attack/articleshow/109344061.cms</guid></item><item><title>与习近平的南海协议：为何菲律宾前总统可能面临叛国罪指控</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/south-china-sea-deal-with-xi-jinping-why-ex-philippine-president-may-face-treason-charges/articleshow/109343205.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109343205.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;前总统杜特尔特因南海协议而面临审查。杜特尔特被指控叛国，与习近平的协议引发了人们对主权和透明度的担忧。随着中国要求拆除 BRP Sierra Madre，紧张局势升级，导致争端进一步恶化。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:06:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/south-china-sea-deal-with-xi-jinping-why-ex-philippine-president-may-face-treason-charges/articleshow/109343205.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈里王子因警察保护案被判支付100万欧元</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/prince-harry-ordered-to-pay-1-million-euros-over-police-protection-case/articleshow/109343912.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109343912.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:04:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/prince-harry-ordered-to-pay-1-million-euros-over-police-protection-case/articleshow/109343912.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国国会议员呼吁采取行动打击美国针对印度教徒的仇恨犯罪不断增加</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-congressman-calls-for-action-against-rising-hate-crimes-against-hindus-in-us/articleshow/109336386.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109336386.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;塔尼达尔对美国的印度教寺庙袭击、仇恨犯罪和执法反应表示担忧。他提出了一项谴责印度恐惧症的决议，并寻求两党支持以打击种族主义。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 06:34:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-congressman-calls-for-action-against-rising-hate-crimes-against-hindus-in-us/articleshow/109336386.cms</guid></item><item><title>对阿米尔·萨法拉兹被杀感到震惊，LeT 召开紧急会议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/shocked-by-elimination-let-calls-emergency-meet/articleshow/109323995.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109323995.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 19:47:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/shocked-by-elimination-let-calls-emergency-meet/articleshow/109323995.cms</guid></item><item><title>国际原子能机构主席格罗西：伊朗因以色列袭击而关闭核设施</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-shut-down-nuclear-facilities-amid-israel-assault-iaea-chief-grossi/articleshow/109334793.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109334793.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国原子能监督机构负责人周一表示，在周末对以色列进行大规模导弹和无人机袭击后，伊朗出于“安全考虑”暂时关闭了其核设施。我可以告诉你的是，伊朗政府通知我们在伊朗的检查人员，昨天（周日），出于安全考虑，我们每天检查的所有核设施将继续关闭。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 05:47:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-shut-down-nuclear-facilities-amid-israel-assault-iaea-chief-grossi/articleshow/109334793.cms</guid></item><item><title>最高法院听取有关妨碍司法的辩论，对特朗普和 1 月 6 日骚乱者的指控岌岌可危</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/charges-against-trump-and-jan-6-rioters-at-stake-as-supreme-court-hears-debate-over-obstruction-law/articleshow/109334299.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109334299.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;最高法院正在考虑可能影响前总统唐纳德·特朗普因试图推翻 2020 年大选而受到刑事起诉的案件。国会大厦骚乱的数百项指控也受到威胁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 05:25:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/charges-against-trump-and-jan-6-rioters-at-stake-as-supreme-court-hears-debate-over-obstruction-law/articleshow/109334299.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>